text:
It's never too soon to start thinking about the holidays.

Good thing Mila Kunis is reminding everyone to get our shopping done early. The mother-of-two posted a sultry photo on Instagram wearing her pretty initial dog tag.

You can gift a loved one a Mila Kunis-approved necklace ($134.99) from Mini Mini Jewels,The personalized trend doesn't seem to going anywhere soon.
title: Mila Kunis Wearing Mini Mini Jewels Dainty Dog Tags Make the Perfect Holiday Gift
